<item>
            <title>[HBASE-1127] OOME running randomRead PE (Disable blanket enabling of blockcache)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1127</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Blockcache is misbehaving on TRUNK.  Something is broke.  We OOME about 20% into the randomRead test.  Looking at heap, its all soft references.  Instrumenting the referencequeue, we&apos;re never clearing full gc&apos;ing.  Something is off.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12412439">HBASE-1127</key>
            <summary>OOME running randomRead PE (Disable blanket enabling of blockcache)</summary>
